::Scyther/Incarcinator::

Scyther suddenly stops in the air, slapping his forehead with his 
hand. "Pinsir can't fly, can he?"

Incarcinator shakes his head, looking at Scyther like he was an 
idiot. "Not last time I checked."

"Allright, lets go pick him up." Scyther flies back to Pinsir's 
location, Incarcinator following him. They land, both holding out an 
arm.

"Here, grab on," says Scyther, "We need to get to the battle quick."
